title: Ahsan Iqbal wins PP-54 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Ahsan Iqbal Chaudhary of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz has won the election from Punjab Assembly constituency PP-54 Narowal by securing 33,243 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an independent candidate Syed Saeed-ul-Hassan who bagged 24,950 votes.
Votersâ€™ turnout remained 55.67 percent.
